apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-summary: Creates a new proposal and files an endorsement.  If the user already endorsed another proposal within the facet, move the user's endorsement to the new proposal.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-title: The encoded entity name, e.g. <kbd>Jade:Diff/123456</kbd>. One of <var>title</var> or <var>entitydata</var> is required.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-entit: The type of Jade entity, e.g. <kbd>{"type": "diff", "id": "123456"}</kbd>. One of <var>title</var> or <var>entitydata</var> is required.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-facet: The facet of the entity being labeled.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-label: The relevant new label data, e.g. <kbd>{"damaging":false, "goodfaith": true}</kbd>. See [[mw:Extension:Jade/API]] for more info.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-notes: Notes to save when creating a new proposal. A warning will be raised if a proposal already exists.  Notes will not be automatically overwritten.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-endor: Comment to leave with the endorsement.
A string representing what the user was looking at when they made this judgment.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-param-nomov: If set, do not move an endorsement.  Instead throw an error.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-example: Create a new proposal and endorse it using the <var>title</var> param.
apihelp-jadecreateandendorse-example-2: Create a new proposal and endorse it using the <var>entitydata</var> param.
apihelp-jadesetpreference-summary: Flag a proposed label as the 'consensus' or best option within a facet.

apihelp-jadesetpreference-param-entityda: The type of Jade entity, e.g. <kbd>{"type": "diff", "id": "123456"}</kbd>. One of <var>title</var> or <var>entitydata</var> is required.
apihelp-jadesetpreference-param-labeldat: The relevant label data, e.g. <kbd>{"damaging": false, "goodfaith": true}</kbd>. See [[mw:Extension:Jade/API]] for more info.
apihelp-jadesetpreference-example: Set a specific proposal as preferred using the <var>title</var> param.
apihelp-jadesetpreference-example-2: Set a specific proposal as preferred using the <var>entitydata</var> param.

apihelp-jadeupdateproposal-param-labelda: The relevant label data, e.g. <kbd>{'damaging':false, 'goodfaith': true}</kbd>. See [[mw:Extension:Jade/API]] for more info.
apihelp-jadeupdateproposal-param-notes: The new notes field for the proposal.
